column16: Chris Gimenez grounds into a double play, shortstop Troy Tulowitzki to second baseman Darwin Barney to first baseman Junior Lake.   Tyler Naquin out at 2nd.
Ryan Goins intentionally walks Tyler Naquin.

Michael Martinez reaches on a fielder's choice out, second baseman Darwin Barney to catcher Josh Thole to third baseman Josh Donaldson to pitcher Ryan Goins.   Jose Ramirez out at home.    Lonnie Chisenhall to 3rd.    Michael Martinez to 2nd.
Lonnie Chisenhall singles on a line drive to center fielder Kevin Pillar.   Jose Ramirez to 3rd.
Jose Ramirez singles on a ground ball to left fielder Michael Saunders.
